    "description": "在射击游戏“Grimwalker”中对抗地狱的力量。 使用各种武器参加激动人心的战斗，并使用你的恶魔形态变得更加强大。 探索充满秘密的世界，同时管理资源以求生存。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369630/extras/ea508842371c88a6046db2a8377e0da9.poster.avif?t=1751210174\" width=630 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369630/extras/ea508842371c88a6046db2a8377e0da9.webm?t=1751210174\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369630/extras/ea508842371c88a6046db2a8377e0da9.mp4?t=1751210174\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>使用各种武器，从经典的步枪和手枪到近战武器。适当选择装备是在与恶魔生物的战斗中获胜的关键。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369630/extras/5e5cd5e710a36679f3075c1bca411784.poster.avif?t=1751210174\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369630/extras/5e5cd5e710a36679f3075c1bca411784.webm?t=1751210174\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369630/extras/5e5cd5e710a36679f3075c1bca411784.mp4?t=1751210174\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>这不仅仅是一款射击游戏，还是一个充满了神秘和谜题可以探索的世界。管理你的装备，寻找能让你存活下来的资源。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369630/extras/cf425c3afc949f9a2cb6fce3edf4c62b.poster.avif?t=1751210174\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369630/extras/cf425c3afc949f9a2cb6fce3edf4c62b.webm?t=1751210174\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369630/extras/cf425c3afc949f9a2cb6fce3edf4c62b.mp4?t=1751210174\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>转化成你的恶魔形态，在你的敌人中肆虐。每个人都有自己的极限...作为一个恶魔，你可以忽略自己的极限。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369630/extras/4109ada6b4b8cbcc7a1358cbc28968ad.poster.avif?t=1751210174\" width=630 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369630/extras/4109ada6b4b8cbcc7a1358cbc28968ad.webm?t=1751210174\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369630/extras/4109ada6b4b8cbcc7a1358cbc28968ad.mp4?t=1751210174\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>站起来对抗占领了被遗忘的村庄的恶魔生物大军，并揭开恶魔之谜。",
